Package: shinyInvoice
Title: Shiny App. Pdf Invoice from Rmarkdown
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2023-11-23
Authors@R: c(person("Fernando", "Roa", email = "froao@ufg.br", role = c("aut", "cre") )
             )
Description: Generate an invoice with any of: salary, one-liner costs, grouped costs in a table. Header with
  invoice number, businesses details. Signature and bank account details under table. Pages numbered when more than one.
  Source .json and .Rmd files editable in the app. Includes functions for getting exchange rates.
Depends: R (>= 3.5)
Imports: 
    tibble,
    dplyr,
    quantmod,
    rlang,
    stringr
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Suggests: 
    rmarkdown,
    shiny
SystemRequirements: pandoc (>= 2.0)
URL: 
BugReports: https://github.com/fernandoroa/invoice-public/issues
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
